
To build:

mvn -Dcucumber.installGems=true cuke4duke:cucumber
mvn clean install

To run Tests:

mvn integration-test

To run Cucumber (without recompiling):

mvn cuke4duke:cucumber

Note: I had problems getting cuke4duke installed ok ....

Missing:
----------
1) cuke4duke:cuke4duke:jar:0.4.3

  Try downloading the file manually from the project website.

  Then, install it using the command: 
      mvn install:install-file -DgroupId=cuke4duke -DartifactId=cuke4duke -Dversion=0.4.3 -Dpackaging=jar -Dfile=/path/to/file

So I built the sources and installed it manuall using the command above.

